Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.21,0:01:47.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.38,0:01:53.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Forgive me for getting here so late.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.72,0:01:54.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:01:56.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...Uncle Daisuke's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:56.39,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Umm, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:58.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is it about your father?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.43,0:03:02.87,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Some people have been saying things about Father and Uncle Daisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:08.04,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I figured that one day the time would come when we had to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:11.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Although it came faster than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:19.84,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Your father's death is a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.21,0:03:22.93,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.81,0:03:28.67,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We could never even imagine the cruel and unrelenting world he lives in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.48,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.84,0:03:32.90,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...accept that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.37,0:03:36.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At first I thought of living together with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.78,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I didn't care if I were to lose my life over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}But now I think this is for the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By leaving me behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:49.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}he could keep our memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:55.17,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He can keep the one thing we cherished as support in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.95,0:04:01.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He longed for where I stood and remain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:04.47,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but he could never reach this place with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.73,0:04:08.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Staying far away from each other was our only option.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.83,0:04:11.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We could only return to each other in our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I had been selfish,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:18.19,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'd have ruined his wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.09,0:04:25.82,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm living the life he yearned for in his dreams in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:31.45,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Love isn't all about being together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:34.46,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.09,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Daisuke-san is your father's son from his previous wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.75,0:04:44.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He could endure all his hardships because his little sister lived happily in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.01,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He told me so himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:49.38,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.35,0:04:55.42,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...have something I need to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.08,0:05:05.33,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I give up...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.02,0:05:07.36,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess it's in the blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.50,0:05:14.91,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:18.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I have no chance of finding them even if I turn every stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:25.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujieda-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.20,0:05:29.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen rescued me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.54,0:05:32.11,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm back home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:32.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank god.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:34.65,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.94,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen and Cal-san are trying to kill each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I overheard them talking on the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They meet at 3 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.90,0:05:49.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}They were talking about a place both of them know well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.25,0:05:51.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...both of them know well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:06:00.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal-san is suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:02.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}She had no one to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:06.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji-san, please help them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.37,0:06:08.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Everything will be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.74,0:06:11.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll work something out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:16.85,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujieda-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.07,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sorry about everything that has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.03,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:25.23,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:29.66,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}By tomorrow I won't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:34.49,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}So you can come back here any time you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.78,0:06:39.24,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I love how you laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:45.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you can feel happy like I saw you can, it's fine for you to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Thank you, I'm really grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fujieda-san, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:55.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.12,0:07:04.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll keep waiting for the time when your burdens are gone and you can return to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:07.32,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:08.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...this isn't farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:11.20,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:13.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.63,0:07:16.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.82,0:07:33.68,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Listen up, don't underestimate them because they're just kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.68,0:07:35.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Are you going to kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.62,0:07:38.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll be there shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.54,0:07:44.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't let Mio-san stand in harm's way any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.04,0:07:45.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.16,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think that's what Mio wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.16,0:07:52.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the promise I made to Brother Daisuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.96,0:07:57.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You people are always like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.72,0:08:06.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Shiga-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:08.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The one who shot Daisuke-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.54,0:08:29.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.75,0:08:30.15,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.54,0:08:33.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...the meaning of all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.62,0:08:35.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No meaning whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm just doing it because I want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:38.20,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.72,0:08:41.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What will you leave behind once you're dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}He will be dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.61,0:08:47.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}my flames will have died,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.53,0:08:48.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}and everything will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:50.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:54.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that really all you ever wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:08:57.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes, it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What else would there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:02.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Besides, what about yourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.89,0:09:05.00,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you ever accomplish when you were alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.00,0:09:07.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What did you leave behind when you died?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.09,0:09:08.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}All of you died like trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.69,0:09:13.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.41,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}And so will you one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:22.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will disappear without proof you ever lived or a reason why you were born.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:25.32,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't screw with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:26.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm different from you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.59,0:09:33.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm the invincible Phantom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:45.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I finally found...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.52,0:09:48.56,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...something I can do better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.77,0:09:52.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}A way of life where no one dares to look down on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.16,0:09:58.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I steal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.86,0:10:03.72,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I bring ruin...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:10.04,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want it to be the other way around again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:11:00.07,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I knew you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:06.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you really think this is for the best?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.50,0:11:07.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:09.60,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't be able to shoot Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.60,0:11:12.55,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No, I'll be the one to kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.39,0:11:17.11,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will burden myself with all her agony and wrath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:24.95,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will probably be the saddest person alive when she dies,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:26.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}but I can be the one to mourn for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:30.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's why I will kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:31.43,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.09,0:11:34.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You will lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.10,0:11:37.30,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want to lose you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.26,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.59,0:11:41.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't want you to do it all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.06,0:11:44.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You won't be able to shoot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:52.62,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll stay here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:55.08,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Together we can beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:58.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Please understand, this is my karma.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.78,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If I don't put an end to this,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:03.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will be forever imprisoned by my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll never be free.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.29,0:12:08.93,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen, leave ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:10.69,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'll catch up with you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.69,0:12:13.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Where should I go without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:17.03,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't even know where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.20,0:12:20.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:30.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What should I do to free myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.44,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What is freedom if it's obtained through killing others?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.13,0:12:42.05,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:55.73,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Let's look for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:56.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To find it I will definitely return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.00,0:13:02.86,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Reiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Elen won't be coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.73,0:13:44.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.62,0:13:46.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Because it's my responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:51.36,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To protect her?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.36,0:13:52.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:53.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.66,0:13:57.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It is to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.09,0:14:02.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Many people have been sacrificed before today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:05.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I lied to countless people,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:07.82,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}used them, and killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.56,0:14:10.74,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...for the sole purpose of staying alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.37,0:14:13.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How dare you say such shameless words...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.59,0:14:17.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You're right, Cal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.23,0:14:19.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bear righteous hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.33,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You don't need to point your gun at anybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.39,0:14:24.80,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Punish me with that gun of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:26.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Don't leave it to someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:27.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do it on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.86,0:14:31.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you're stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.97,0:14:34.51,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}retribution will be brought down upon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.99,0:14:37.48,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.56,0:15:00.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I won't let you get in their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:01.79,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.12,0:15:09.63,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you really want to resolve everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.65,0:15:13.13,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}let this decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:14.23,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:16.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh, so you recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.40,0:15:20.17,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This is the fate we share.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.17,0:15:22.10,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}This has cast light on my path until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.01,0:15:28.57,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It was always there to tell me whom to hate or whom to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:38.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The duel is with handguns.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.83,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}We draw when the song ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.78,0:15:46.50,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The only one who's heard this song and not been killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.25,0:15:52.01,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...is you, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.76,0:16:59.53,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What? Were you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.64,0:17:03.61,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I had a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.54,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...of when we were still in L.A..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:07.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Oh? What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:16.18,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What would have happened to us if we had been separated after our hideout was blown?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.30,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That sounds stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.30,0:17:22.27,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You wouldn't make such a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.09,0:17:27.56,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's impossible for us to be separated.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.22,0:17:32.12,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If it did happen, I'd look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.12,0:17:34.41,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To the end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:37.99,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}No way it could happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:43.29,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I really am stupid beyond salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:48.25,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I say such things...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.88,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}It's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:55.26,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.38,0:17:59.66,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Isn't it fine this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.75,0:18:02.53,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}At least it would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.64,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...if I could find the unlikely salvation I dream of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.75,0:18:21.83,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is this where Judy Devens died?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.81,0:18:32.31,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}How can you be so strong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.13,0:18:37.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I can only answer you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.58,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.58,0:18:40.99,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.40,0:18:48.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I did manage to have you for myself in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.93,0:18:52.42,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Then I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.07,0:18:56.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I don't need anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:02.27,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is that the reason you threw your life away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:05.75,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.77,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Is there any more reason than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:18.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Do you think we could have lived a different life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:25.38,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Met under different circumstances and lived somewhere far away?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.76,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Yeah, we just...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.03,0:19:31.90,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...took a wrong turn somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.14,0:19:34.02,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.39,0:19:40.98,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm glad I met you, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.40,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}That's all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:45.85,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.87,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I'm happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.29,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.36,0:20:09.09,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:14.28,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,1600)}Cal!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:35.94,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Phantom... you monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:46.21,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Sheesh, I fail to understand your lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:52.96,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I was expecting you to be smarter than this, Mr. Shiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.96,0:20:56.65,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Why didn't you leave everything to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:21:01.35,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}You bastard! Were you just watching from the sidelines until now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:03.88,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The stage has reached the epilogue at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:07.49,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Unrefined extras aren't welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.47,0:21:12.70,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}If you don't mind, vacate the premises and watch from the side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.56,0:21:19.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Consider it an honor; this public performance will be my masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:23.67,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}The concerto of the ultimate phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.92,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:28.59,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}who will answer the curtain call, I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.35,0:21:45.14,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.44,0:21:47.61,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:50.54,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}To keep on living,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:53.89,Phantom-night,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}I will kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:35.50,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Even though I've made lots of mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.50,0:23:39.89,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}...and failed to keep many promises in my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.89,0:23:43.34,Phantom-day,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}there is one promise I must keep no matter what.
